        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2> <a href="/home/products/2">  Food Shop </a>  </h2>
        <p>
            <img width="300" height="200" src="~/Upload/fastfood.jpg" />

        </p>
    </div>
</div>